{"tid":1877373,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中国海警防疫不忘「繞島」  日本人憤怒：救援口罩還來！","createTime":"2020-02-13T03:34:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-13T04:05:45.000Z","uid":184679,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"eccc31816b37a9f195552398a5bd160397eb5d5e","tid":1877373,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T03:34:08.000Z","msg":"由新型冠狀病毒（2019-nCoV）所引起之肺炎「 COVID-19 」，簡稱為「武漢肺炎」，根據新浪網數據，截至北京時間今日（ 12 ）上午 9 點，中國各省確診病例已超過 4 萬 4 千例，死亡病例共 1,114 例，超過 20 個國家受到疫情影響，其中日本因爲橫濱港外停靠的郵輪鑽石公主號，確診病例不斷飆升，船上已有 174 人感染。<br />\n<br />\n根據《 NHK 》，正當各國衛生單位忙得焦頭爛額之時，日本第 11 管區海上保安部證實，中國海警的 4 艘船隻在，沖繩附近的釣魚台列嶼（日本稱為尖閣諸島）附近繞行，日本海岸警隊總部發出警告，使其遠離海域。<br />\n<br />\n釣魚台列嶼的主權目前仍處於爭議狀態，中、台、日三方皆稱擁有該島。<br />\n<br />\n對於各國正忙著防疫，疫情發源地的中國海警的舉動引起了日本人的不滿，特別是前天（ 10 ）自民黨幹事長二階俊博在記者會上表示，將向中國提供支援資金。更早之前，7 日凌晨，日本政府的包機又將一批支援物資運到武漢市，這批支援物資的箱子上寫著「加油！武漢」、「中國，加油！」等標語。<br />\n<br />\n日本網友在推特上評論炸裂，表示「這就是支援武漢的結局。很明顯浪費了人道救援。」、「在日本完全買不到口罩了，如果爆發感染，日本人該怎麼辦？和中國關係好的國家，俄羅斯、北韓、伊朗都禁止中國人入境。美國、台灣、澳洲也是！日本卻還沒有作為（除了湖北、浙江）日本政府這麼信任中國提供的情報，日本的安全真的是糟糕了」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/euRWGFGSEccdJgASuWPoGA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9Njk2O2g9OTI4/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/nownews.com/9e4e4bbffc3951db6d5b1c15ac277003\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FeuRWGFGSEccdJgASuWPoGA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9Njk2O2g9OTI4%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fnownews.com%2F9e4e4bbffc3951db6d5b1c15ac277003&h=60631d55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/MVNpBaOH.ca0jhYZmZOQ5w--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9Njk2O2g9NTEw/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/nownews.com/e8ed6643f825d58914f9c4a72a955957\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FMVNpBaOH.ca0jhYZmZOQ5w--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9Njk2O2g9NTEw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fnownews.com%2Fe8ed6643f825d58914f9c4a72a955957&h=6f174025&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n此外自民黨幹事長二階堂也成為眾矢之的，網友們抨擊支援中國口罩、防護服、資金卻得到這樣的結果，簡直就是被「恩將仇報」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Ae6wwAG4kPTChHwcx.u0GA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTkwO2g9MTMz/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/nownews.com/8b9dd684a539e96596e548edcac95a7f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FAe6wwAG4kPTChHwcx.u0GA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTkwO2g9MTMz%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fnownews.com%2F8b9dd684a539e96596e548edcac95a7f&h=fe1140e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8%E6%B5%B7%E8%AD%A6%E9%98%B2%E7%96%AB%E4%B8%8D%E5%BF%98-%E7%B9%9E%E5%B3%B6-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91-%E6%95%91%E6%8F%B4%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E9%82%84%E7%B5%A6%E6%88%91%E5%90%A7-092057000.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2599%25B8%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%2598%25B2%25E7%2596%25AB%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25BF%2598-%25E7%25B9%259E%25E5%25B3%25B6-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591-%25E6%2595%2591%25E6%258F%25B4%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%25E9%2582%2584%25E7%25B5%25A6%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%2590%25A7-092057000.html&d=2Od897eOL%2Byk6rGVR7zebRSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=a661a14a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8%E6%B5%B7%E8%AD%A6%E9%98%B2%E7%96%AB%E4%B8%8D%E5%BF%98-%E7%B9%9E%E5%B3%B6-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91-%E6%95%91%E6%8F%B4%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E9%82%84%E7%B5%A6%E6%88%91%E5%90%A7-092057000.html</a>"},{"pid":"f9c1a583e4f58e1746d8b7a81cadc3699709a88c","tid":1877373,"uid":237562,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T03:35:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">暴支膺懲</span>"},{"pid":"8dccd5850dc725b050cc96a93c72681e4f89838a","tid":1877373,"uid":105976,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020